\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces Soil transported per episode ($W_2$ between the episode's initial and final soil states) over reward-free training. Rolling mean over 100 episodes. The rise from $\approx 0.03$\,m (ambient settling --- what the soil does with a motionless arm) to $\approx 0.28$\,m is digging being \emph  {invented}.}}{17}{figure.2}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:learning}{{2}{17}{Soil transported per episode ($W_2$ between the episode's initial and final soil states) over reward-free training. Rolling mean over 100 episodes. The rise from $\approx 0.03$\,m (ambient settling --- what the soil does with a motionless arm) to $\approx 0.28$\,m is digging being \emph {invented}}{figure.2}{}}
