\newlabel{fig:demo}{{6}{20}{The zero-shot shaping demo in full: per-target profiles (initial / target / achieved), simulator frames mid- and end-execution, and the contraction curves. No reward, no planner, no goal-conditioned training --- composition of reward-free skills via latent steering}{figure.6}{}}
